3\" height=\"1024\" src=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/srobe-4-1-843x1024.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"8711\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/srobe-4-1.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/?attachment_id=8711\" class=\"wp-image-8711\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/srobe-4-1-843x1024.jpg 843w, https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/srobe-4-1-247x300.jpg 247w, https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/srobe-4-1-768x932.jpg 768w, https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/srobe-4-1.jpg 1242w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 843px) 100vw, 843px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><\/ul><\/figure>\n\n\n\n<figure class=\"wp-block-gallery columns-2 is-cropped\"><ul class=\"blocks-gallery-grid\"><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"548\" height=\"366\" src=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/oktoberbest.png\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"8698\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/oktoberbest.png\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/?attachment_id=8698\" class=\"wp-image-8698\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/oktoberbest.png 548w, https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/oktoberbest-300x200.png 300w\" sizes=\"(max-width: 548px) 100vw, 548px\" \/><\/figure><\/li><li class=\"blocks-gallery-item\"><figure><img loading=\"lazy\" width=\"1024\" height=\"497\" src=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/AWA-1024x497.jpg\" alt=\"\" data-id=\"8704\" data-full-url=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/AWA.jpg\" data-link=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/?attachment_id=8704\" class=\"wp-image-8704\" srcset=\"https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/AWA-1024x497.jpg 1024w, https:\/\/www.fluentco.com\/wp-content\/uploads\/2020\/08\/AWA-300x146.